{"Header":{"nav":{"about":"About Us","products":"Products","projects":"Projects","contacts":"Contacts"},"menu":"Menu"},"Footer":{"quickLinks":"Quick Links","nav":{"about":"About Us","products":"Products","projects":"Projects","contacts":"Contacts"},"contactInfo":{"title":"Contact Details","address":"17 Kuishi Dina Str, Astana, Kazakhstan","email":"istock@istock.kz","phone":"+7 (7172) 251-575"},"copyright":"© 2026 ISTOCK GROUP."},"Images":{"title1":"Explore our comprehensive catalog of reagents for all industrial sectors.","subtitle1":"PRODUCTS AND SOLUTIONS","link1":"/products#Products","title2":"Visit our state-of-the-art production facility in Karaganda.","subtitle2":"OUR MANUFACTURING","link2":"/about#ImageText","title3":"DIOXEL®: Innovative water disinfection technologies.","subtitle3":"TECHNOLOGIES OF THE FUTURE","link3":"/products#Dioxel","button":"Learn More"},"Hero":{"label":"KAZAKHSTANI MANUFACTURER","headline":"ISTOCK Group is a leader in manufacturing chemicals and equipment for industrial water treatment. We preserve water quality for the future.","cards":[{"category":"OUR MANUFACTURING","title":"Own production site in Karaganda, meeting global chemical industry standards."},{"category":"INNOVATION","title":"DIOXEL® — high-performance chlorine dioxide generators of our own production."},{"category":"EXPERTISE","title":"Comprehensive technical audits and professional engineering support for your projects."},{"category":"PARTNERSHIP","title":"Tailored solutions for industry leaders: ANPZ, AlES, KazMunayGas, and many others."}]},"Services":{"subtitle":"Our qualified engineers provide end-to-end project support","title":"Our Services","cta":"Contact Us","items":[{"title":"Technological Concept Development","list":["Process flow diagrams.","Feasibility studies.","Pilot project launches."]},{"title":"Project Implementation (EPCM)","list":["Project management.","Equipment procurement.","Installation management.","Supervision and commissioning.","Staff training."]},{"title":"Chemical Services","list":["Reagent supply.","Dosage selection.","Equipment calibration.","Service and process chemicalization."]},{"title":"Maintenance & Support","list":["Equipment servicing.","Performance adjustment.","Spare parts supply.","Training and consultation."]},{"title":"Chemical Production","list":["Integrated approach to reagent production for:\nClarification.\nSoftening.\nDesalination."]},{"title":"DIOXEL®","list":["Highly efficient chlorine dioxide generators manufactured in Kazakhstan with extended service life."]}]},"Companies":{"title":"Our Partners and Clients","label":"PARTNERS"},"ContactUs":{"main":{"title":"Need a consultation?","linkText":"Contact Us"},"about":{"title":"Would you like to visit our production facility?","linkText":"Yes!"},"products":{"title":"Want to learn more about our products?","linkText":"Contact Us"},"projects":{"title":"Ready to cooperate?","linkText":"Contact Us"},"contacts":{"title":"Have any questions?","linkText":"Contact Us"}},"OfficeStatus":{"open":"Offices are currently open","willOpenIn":"Offices will open in","hour":"hour","hours":"hours"},"AboutPage":{"hero":{"label":"OUR MISSION","title":"Leading the Way in Water Treatment","subtitle":"We implement advanced water and wastewater treatment technologies to ensure industrial safety and environmental sustainability."},"TextHero":{"title":"ISTOCK Group of Companies","content":"We are a leading Kazakhstani manufacturer of chemicals, reagents, and equipment for water treatment systems. Our goal is to provide effective solutions for the most complex water treatment challenges for industrial enterprises across Kazakhstan and beyond."},"ImageText":{"title":"Our Own Production","content":"The ISTOCK Solutions production site is located in Karaganda and meets all the strict requirements for first-class chemical manufacturing. This allows us to personally control the quality of every liter of reagent and ensure efficient logistics."}},"ProductsPage":{"hero":{"label":"PRODUCTS","title":"Our Products","subtitle":"Chemicals and reagents manufactured in Kazakhstan."},"TextHero":{"title":"Why Our Products","content":"Our own production site allows us to control the quality of our products, developed to be as effective as possible for each individual consumer."},"ProductGrid":{"subtitle":"REAGENT CATALOG","title":"High-Performance Chemical Solutions","cta":"Get a Consultation","items":[{"title":"Coagulants","list":["Range of organic and inorganic coagulants","Effective across wide temperature and pH ranges","Optimal water clarification and treatment"]},{"title":"Flocculants","list":["Wastewater, process water, and drinking water treatment","Thickening and dewatering of sludge and sediment","Enrichment of coal, ores, and minerals"]},{"title":"Biodispersants","list":["Removal of biological and hydrocarbon films","Inhibition of anaerobic bacteria growth","Protection of equipment surfaces and pipelines"]},{"title":"Scale Inhibitors","list":["Prevention of sulfate and carbonate deposits","Protection of internal equipment surfaces","Highly effective dispersant function"]},{"title":"Corrosion Inhibitors","list":["Protection for ferrous and non-ferrous metals","Reduction of corrosion rates","Extended equipment service life"]},{"title":"Bactericides","list":["Suppression of microbiological corrosion","Control of aerobic and anaerobic bacteria","Reduction of biofilm formation"]},{"title":"Oxygen Scavengers","list":["Steam condensate system protection","Corrosion inhibitor for high-pressure boilers","Effective removal of dissolved oxygen"]},{"title":"Defoamers","list":["Prevention of foaming in technical systems","Surface-active aqueous solutions","Stability across a wide range of conditions"]},{"title":"Membrane Cleaning","list":["Extended service life for reverse osmosis systems","Removal of complex organic contaminants","Compatibility with membranes from any manufacturer"]}]},"ImageText":{"title":"DIOXEL®","content":"Water disinfection with chlorine dioxide is a highly effective and gentle method for combating Legionella bacteria and all types of pathogenic microorganisms in water, such as viruses, parasites, and fungal spores.\n\nISTOCK Solutions manufactures and supplies DIOXEL® chlorine dioxide production and dosing units for effective and safe water disinfection.","cta":"Learn More"}},"ProjectsPage":{"hero":{"label":"PROJECTS","title":"Projects and Partners","subtitle":"Reputation is a core component of success. Our experience and high level of responsibility towards our clients allow us to guarantee the high quality of technical solutions at every stage."},"TextHero":{"title":"Projects and Partners","content":"The ISTOCK engineering department specializes in the implementation of comprehensive water and wastewater treatment projects. Using a personalized approach, we offer cutting-edge technical solutions."},"Solutions":{"label":"Manufacturing Company","title":"Individual Solutions","content":"On a manufacturing scale, we remain committed to high quality and extreme attention to every partner. Successful pilot industrial trials at ANPZ LLP and AlES JSC confirm the reliability of our technologies. We value our reputation and are fully responsible for product quality at every stage of its application.","cta":"Request an Audit","cards":[{"title":"Mining Industry","description":"Mining operations generate highly contaminated mine and quarry waters. The composition of mine water varies greatly in pollutants, making its use for technical purposes or discharge into water bodies impossible without preliminary treatment."},{"title":"Metallurgy and Energy","description":"Water treatment in energy and metallurgy is a key stage in the production chain of all energy facilities. The uninterrupted operation of CHP, NPP, GRES, and boiler house equipment depends on water quality."},{"title":"Chemical Industry and Oil Refining","description":"Water treatment in the chemical industry is essential to minimize the impact of water on equipment (mechanical damage, deposits, various types of corrosion). Wastewater treatment helps reduce environmental impact."},{"title":"Drinking Water Supply","description":"The life and health of people depend on the quality of water treatment at water utilities. Primarily, water is treated to prevent the development of epidemiological diseases and avoid negative impacts on human health. Additionally, ensuring equipment safety and low process costs are crucial."}]},"Companies":{"title":"Our Partners and Clients","label":"PARTNERS"}},"ContactsPage":{"title":"Contacts","subtitle":"Get in Touch","number":"+7 (7172) 251-575","email":"istock@istock.kz","mapHint":"Click to interact","info":{"solutions":{"title":"ISTOCK Solutions LLP","name":"Askar Musin","email":"istock@istock.kz"},"chemi":{"title":"ISTOCK CHEMI LLP","name":"Ramazan Alimbetov","email":"istock@istock.kz"},"water":{"title":"ISTOCK Water Technologies & Solutions LLP","name":"Raimbek Maratov","email":"office@istock.kz"}},"office":{"title":"Office in Astana","address":"17 KUISHI DINA STR."}}}